Need help?

If you can't find the home

Try using Google Maps, Apple Maps, or Waze. Call us at 800-544-0300 if you're still unable to find the home.

If you need help with the lockbox or keypad

Our guide to lockboxes and smart locks can help. If you're still having trouble, call us at 800-544-0300.

If you can't connect to the internet

Unplug the router, then wait two minutes and plug it back in. Wait another two to five minutes before you try to connect.

Review or update your reservation

You can visit your Trip Manager or the Vacasa mobile app to view your reservation details and make changes to your trip, like:

  • Update the number of guests
  • View driving directions and parking instructions
  • See a list of the homes amenities, including WiFi information
  • Review check-in and check-out instructions

Cancel your reservation

If you need to cancel your reservation for any reason, our worry-free booking policy allows you to do so easily. Under this policy, you can cancel your reservation online up until 30 days before check-in (or cancel for credit at any time, if your check-in date is through August 31).

  • You can cancel and receive a Future Stay Credit for 100% of your reservation cost. The credit is flexible, so youre free to book the same home as before, or visit a different Vacasa home or destination.

Cancel and receive credit ›

  • You also have the option to cancel and receive a refund (minus the booking fee) in your Trip Manager.
